56
00:03:56,290 --> 00:03:58,250
"Ew"? You don't need to—

57
00:03:59,510 --> 00:04:01,470
Hello, Onii-san.

58
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:03,720
Thanks for your help last time.

59
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:05,890
No, don't mention it.

60
00:04:05,890 --> 00:04:07,850
